 * <br />
 * Note that in this function, if query exists exactly at the end of the argument text, it is not regarded as being followed by an empty string, and no empty string is stored in the last element of the returned array.
 * This behavior differs from splitText, but it will not be changed in order to preserve compatibility.
 *
 * @param text The target string.
 * @param query The delimiter string, which is not included in the contents of the resulting string array.
